@startuml
title Proxy de cache - consultas costosas
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  interface ReportRepository <<Subject>> {
+findById(id: String): String
  }
  class DatabaseReportRepository <<RealSubject>>
  class CachedReportProxy <<Proxy>>
}

ReportRepository <|.. DatabaseReportRepository
ReportRepository <|.. CachedReportProxy
CachedReportProxy --> DatabaseReportRepository : controla/delega
Main ..> ReportRepository : usa misma interfaz

note bottom of CachedReportProxy
Evita llamadas repetidas al sujeto real cuando ya existe una respuesta cacheada.
end note
@enduml
